nd do away with the dreaded =E2=80=98local market blackout.=E2=80=99 Please=
 just let me give someone money to stream the Braves in Nashville. I=E2=80=
=99m running out of things to watch when Copa America and the Euros are ove=
r and don=E2=80=99t know if I can make it to the Olympics.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=
=94Another finance exec

